This extension needs to be compiled and enabled in your PHP installation.

Basic instructions:

1) phpize
2) ./configure
3) make && make install

For Debian/Ubuntu users:

The following packages need to be installed before running the steps above:

1) php5-dev
2) libpcre3-dev
3) libavro (https://launchpad.net/~chris-lea/+archive/avro)
3) libcurl4-openssl-dev
